				<div class="fd_com_linebreak">searchOption [true / false] - > 
					<br>
					<div class="fd_com_subcontent">True : Will result in dropdown along with search box.</div>
					<div class="fd_com_subcontent">False :  Will result in normal dropdown without search box</div>
				</div> 
				<div class="fd_com_linebreak">
					subDropDown,itemDropDown ->
					<div class="fd_com_subcontent"> By default, Dropdown 2 and Dropdown 3 will be in hidden state.</div> 
					<div class="fd_com_subcontent">Dropdown(2,3) Based on Dropdown 1</div>
				</div>
				<div class="fd_com_linebreak">
					category,subcategory,item -> 
					<div class="fd_com_subcontent">Model(s) which holds the dropdown selection. Later we can use it in controller</div> 
